channel.title: Hamachi
channel.description:
I'm trying to get my rsps on with hamachi,
at first I've zipped my cache and maked a client.jar of it.
after that I've in client.java changed localhost to my hamachi-ip
people logged in on my hamachi but it still gives error to connection !
I'm running it on port 43595.
for me it's just working... I don't know why not for others.
